Volks,

Made a silly mistake that caused me to have low oil pressure on my 1776 =
motor.  I used the thick paper gasket between the pump cover and the =
pump instead of the thin one.....went fron 4lbs pressure at idle to =
15-20 warm. =20

If it worked out this way more often!
